item.title: CVE-2022-4349|2024-08-03T01:34:50.101Z -- ctf-hacker -- pwn
item.description: A vulnerability classified as problematic has been found in CTF-hacker pwn. This affects an unknown part of the file delete.html. The manipulation leads to cross-site request forgery. It is possible to initiate the attack remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used. The identifier VDB-215109 was assigned to this vulnerability.
